Privacy Policy for Flavor Fusion

Effective Date: 13 Oct, 2023

1. Introduction

Welcome to Flavor Fusion! This Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our mobile application, Flavor Fusion. By downloading, installing, and using our app, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.

2. Information We Collect

No Personal Data: Flavor Fusion does not collect or store any personal data, such as your name, email address, phone number, or location information.

3. How We Use Your Information

Improvement: The usage data we collect helps us analyze how our app is used and identify areas for improvement.

App Functionality: We use information to provide and enhance the functionality of the app.

4. Information Sharing

No Third-Party Sharing: We do not share any information with third parties.


7. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or change this Privacy Policy at any time. Any modifications will be posted within the app. Your continued use of the app after such changes are made constitutes your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at usamajaved1119@gmail.com.

By using Flavor Fusion, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.
